name: Sandeep Londhe
body:
I am a Software Engineer, Consultant, Trainer & Android Enthusiast. Currently Living in Mumbai, Maharashtra, India. My Interests range from Android to Java. I am also interested in Php, ios, and Women.

I love to code in Java, I am a fan of Open Source Website Development. In the free time I blog on different topics on Mobile Development, Open Source. I Love to share Knowledge. Hire me if you want to make an Android or iOS App.
